'''聖馬太大學'''（{{lang-en|St. Matthew's University}}，缩写为SMU）是一所位於[[開曼群島|開曼群島]][[大開曼|大開曼]]的[[營利學校|盈利性大學]]。有授予[[醫學士|醫學士]]（{{lang|en|MD}}）和獸醫學士（{{lang|en|DVM}}）的資格。已受到開曼群島政府的認可。<ref name="Cayman" /> 但美國 <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mbc.ca.gov/applicant/schools_unapproved.html|title=Medical Board of California - International Medical Schools Disapproved by the State of California|work=mbc.ca.gov|accessdate=2011-09-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216095721/http://www.mbc.ca.gov/applicant/schools_unapproved.html|archivedate=2012-02-16}}</ref>和英國的一些醫學研究機構並不認可該大學的證書。

== 歷史==

[[File:St_Matthews_2.jpg|thumb]]

該大學1997年由美國[[大福克斯_(北達科他州)|大福克斯]]人Jeffrey S. Sersland創立於[[伯利茲|伯利茲]]，其名稱是爲了紀念其好友Matthew Uhrich。<ref name="sanpedrosun2004">{{Cite web |url=http://sanpedrosun.net/old/04-194.html |title=Our Community - Dr. Jeffrey Sersland - sanpedrosun.net - June 10, 2004 |accessdate=2013-11-19 |archive-date=2011-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930104804/http://sanpedrosun.net/old/04-194.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2001年因董事會決議撤銷Sersland和其妻子的職務。次年搬至開曼群島。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sanpedrosun.net/old/01-233.html |title=St. Matthew's changes administration - sanpedrosun.net - June 14, 2001 |accessdate=2013-11-19 |archive-date=2011-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930104825/http://sanpedrosun.net/old/01-233.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

大學的獸醫學院（School of Veterinary Medicine）建立於2005年。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stmatthews.edu/about_history.shtml |title=St. Matthew's University | About St Matthew's University | History of St. Matthew's University |publisher=Stmatthews.edu |date=2005-09-01 |accessdate=2010-03-16 |archive-date=2008-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080323234758/http://stmatthews.edu/about_history.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

